# Setup Frontend Design Sub-Skill

## Overview

This sub-skill guides the creation of the `/midtempo-framework/instructions/frontend-design.md` file through structured dialogue and codebase analysis.

**Goal:** Create frontend-design.md documenting component architecture, composition patterns, and UI organisation methodology.

**Target:** 300-400 lines total, regardless of component library size. Focus on architectural patterns over component catalogues, composition rules over exhaustive listings.

**Scope:** This file documents COMPONENT ARCHITECTURE and COMPOSITION PATTERNS (Design Structure, Container/Presentational, Compound Components, component organisation). {% if capabilities.hasUI %}Visual styling (colours, spacing, typography), is in a different document.{% endif %}

